@0 = ~ Who are you? What do you want? ~
@1 = ~ I'm <CHARNAME>, looking for an old magician here, I was sent here by the high priest of the city of priests. ~
@2 = ~ So you're probably looking for me. I was recently sought out by a group led by a gnome, but I managed to hide right before their arrival. ~
@3 = ~ They are dead, I took care of them. ~
@4 = ~ But who said you are better than others. What do you want from me? ~
@5 = ~ I'm here on behalf of the shadow lord Deepwater. He wants to talk to you. ~
@6 = ~ Okay, I will listen to him. I will teleport us to the city. ~
